01:01:45,640 --> 01:01:47,995
Why don't you
get the hell out of here?

717
01:01:48,080 --> 01:01:50,355
Get the fuck away from me, man.

718
01:02:05,920 --> 01:02:10,072
Very good, Victor. Could you teach
him to roll over and sit, too?

719
01:02:11,480 --> 01:02:13,835
- What do you want?
- l wanna talk to you.

720
01:02:13,920 --> 01:02:17,833
- Last time, l didn't get the chance.
- l've nothing to say to you.

721
01:02:18,200 --> 01:02:20,555
That's cool, l'll do all the talking.

722
01:02:21,760 --> 01:02:24,035
This is a very nice place, Vic.

723
01:02:24,600 --> 01:02:27,239
Hi. l like this. This is nice.

724
01:02:28,120 --> 01:02:31,078
Glad you like it.
l must make you a member.

725
01:02:33,520 --> 01:02:37,832
Victor, l know that you're into
a lot of crooked shit.

726
01:02:37,920 --> 01:02:41,230
And l have a pretty good idea
that you had Mikey killed.

727
01:02:41,320 --> 01:02:44,039
And when l find out for sure,

728
01:02:44,120 --> 01:02:46,190
l'm going to fuck you up real bad.

729
01:02:46,280 --> 01:02:48,236
ls that so?

730
01:02:48,320 --> 01:02:51,392
Now listen to me,
my tough little friend.

731
01:02:51,480 --> 01:02:55,189
l don't know
from under what stone you crawled

732
01:02:55,280 --> 01:02:58,590
or where you get
these ridiculous ideas about me,

733
